  40 醫師: Lau7-ia5, li2 na7 ai3 oah8-mia7 li2 tioh8 ai3 chun-tiong7 i-hak8-siong7 e5 kui-ku2, m7-thang tin2-tang7, tioh8 choat8-tui3 e5 an-cheng7. 
  41 富人: Goa2 hian7-si5 bo5 hit e5 u5-te7 thang koh thiaN jim7-ho5 e5 hak8-soat. ChhiaN2 lin2 hou7 goa2 khia7 khi2-lai5. (khia7 khi2-lai5) Goa2 sit8-chai7 chin-gong7, goa2 an2-choaN2 lou2-lek8 lai5 kian3-lip8 goa2 e5 ka-giap8, siat-su2 goa2 na7 an2-ne lai5 si2, goa2 e5 cho3 lang5 kiam2 m7-si7 chin m7-tat8 mah? Sou2-i2 goa2 su-iau3 tiong5-sin e5 oah8-mia7, thang hiong2-siu7 jin5-seng, tu2-tu2 chiau3 goa2 e5 hu-jin5-lang5 sou2 kian3-gi7 e5...... 
