  第四幕 
  出場人物: 拉撒路, 天使a, 天使b, 米勒, 以東. 
  場面: 富人的大門口 (和第二幕同樣) 開幕: 拉撒路在黑暗的雪夜中在祈禱吟聖詩236首的第四節 
  1 拉撒路: Ia5-ho5-hoa goa2 e5 chou2 A-pek-liap8-han2, I2-sat, Nga2-kok e5 Siong7-te3 ah, Li2 chai7-cha2 an2-choaN2 eng7 Li2 e5 koan5-leng5 ki5-su7 in2-chhoa7 Li2 e5 peh-seN3 thoat-chhut Ai-kip8 e5 heng5-hoat8, in2-chhoa7 goan2 e5 chou2 keng-koe3 Ang5-hai2, lek8-iu5 40 ni5 ti7 khong3-han7 e5 soa-bou5 tiong, tui3 tui3-tek8 e5 chhiu2, tui3 che7-che7 kan-lan5 Li2 u7 in2-chhoa7 in kau3 ti7 Li2 sou2 eng3-un2 e5 Ka-lam5 lai5, ti7 lau5 ni, lau5 bit8 e5 Ka-lam5 toe7, Li2 hou7 goan2 e5 chou2 toa7-toa7 heng-khi2, soa3 ti7 chit e5 toe7 kian3-lip8 in e5 ong5-kok. Li2 u7 ku2-khi2 Li2 e5 peh-seN3, chhin-chhiuN7 eng5-iau7 e5 ki5 ti7 liat8-pang tiong. Khiok ti7 un-tian2 e5 jit8 goan2 e5 chou2 soa3 poe7-gek8 Li2, khi3 kui7-pai3 goa7-pang e5 ngou2-siong7, kap put-sin3 e5 peh-seN3 saN-chhin, kiat-iok, ti3-kau3 jia2-tioh8 li2 e5 siu7-khi3, kok-bong5, bin5-pai7, kau3 kin-a2-jit8 soa3 ti7 goa7-pang e5 chhiu2-e7, chiaN5-cho3 goa7-pang sou2 thun2-tah8 e5 mih8. 
  Ah, goa2 e5 Chu2, goa2 e5 Siong7-te3 ah, Li2 beh pang3-sak Li2 e5 peh-seN3 kau3 sim2-mih8 si5 ah! Kiu5 Li2 koh chit8-pai2 eng7 Li2 e5 chhoe5 lai5 piN-phah in, hou7 in oe7 hoe2-kai2 chhiN2-gou7 lai5 kui-ng3 Li2. Kiu5 Li2 kin2-kin2 kiu3-siok8 goan2. 
  Kiu5 Li2 ia7 ki3-liam7 Li2 siu7-khou2 e5 kiaN2-ji5 long2-chong2 e5 au5-kio3, kiu5 Li2 sia3-bian2 goa2 ti7 chit e5 oah8-lang5 e5 toe7 sou2 u7 boe7-thang eng5-iau7 Li2 e5 seng-oah8. 
  Kiu5 Li2 chiap-lap8 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5 kui ti7 Li2 eng2-oan2 thiaN3 kiaN2 e5 kok. A-men. 
  (吟聖詩244首第一節, gim5-liau2 khai-si2 thang3-thiaN3) 
  Goa2 e5 Chu2, goa2 e5 Siong7-te3 ah, kiu5 Li2 chiap-lap8 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5. Oh, goa2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 thiN-khui eng5-kng chhan3-lan7 e5 thou2-te7, thiN-sai3 chu7-chip8 ti7 hia. Oh, goa2 sou2 him-bou7 e5 chou2-ke! (拉撒路死, 聖歌隊繼續吟244首2節, 有2個天使出現) 
  2 天使a: Siu7-khou2 e5 kiaN2 Liap8-sat-lou7, Ia5-ho5-hoa, li2 e5 Chu2,li2 e5 Siong7-te3, i2-keng kam3-chhat li2 khun3-lan5 e5 jit8-chi2, khoaN3-kiN3 li2 e5 jim2-siu7. Li2 ti7 kek8-ki5 pi-chham2 e5 jit8 iau2-ku2 jiat8-jiat8 e5 sim sin3-giong2 Chu2 li2 e5 Siong7-te3, giah8-bak8 ng3-thiN tan2-hau7 I e5 kok, taN Chu2 li2 e5 Siong7-te3 beh chiap-lap8 leng5-hun5 kau3 ti7 I thiaN3 kiaN2 e5 kok. 
  3 天使b: HiaN-ti7 Liap8-sat-lou7 ah, li2 e5 siu7-khou2, li2 e5 pi-chham2 long2 soah lah. Li2 m7-bian2 koh ti7 chit e5 chhiN-chhin3, leng2-cheng7 e5 ke-lou7 chiuN7 kou-toaN khun3-khou2 lah. Li2 long2-chong2 e5 bak8-sai2 ia7 soah lah, li2 eng3-kai jip8 ti7 li2 e5 chou2 A-pek-liap8-han2 e5 hoai5-lai7, lai5 tit-tioh8 an-hioh. 
